# RP6502 Learning Documentation Resources

When working on RP6502-related tasks, use the following documentation resources in priority order:

## Primary RP6502 Documentation

1. **Picocomputer Official Documentation** - https://picocomputer.github.io/index.html
   - Main documentation site for RP6502
   - Hardware: https://picocomputer.github.io/hardware.html
   - RP6502-RIA: https://picocomputer.github.io/ria.html
   - RP6502-VGA: https://picocomputer.github.io/vga.html
   - RP6502-OS: https://picocomputer.github.io/os.html
   - Use for: Hardware specs, RIA/VGA features, OS API, memory maps, register documentation

2. **Picocomputer GitHub Documentation**
   - Official repository: https://github.com/picocomputer
   - Use for: Source code, examples, community discussions
   - Note: For RP6502-specific documentation, use the official website (resource 1)

## Raspberry Pi Pico Foundation Documentation

3. **Raspberry Pi Microcontrollers Documentation** - https://www.raspberrypi.com/documentation/microcontrollers/
   - Official Raspberry Pi microcontroller documentation
   - Use for: General RP2040/Pico hardware information, getting started guides

4. **Pico SDK Documentation** - https://www.raspberrypi.com/documentation/pico-sdk/
   - Official Pico SDK API reference
   - Use for: SDK functions, hardware APIs, programming guides

## Educational Resources

6. **Raspberry Pi Pico Lectures 2025** - https://ece4760.github.io/
   - Cornell ECE4760 course materials
   - Use for: PIO examples, VGA drivers, communication protocols, algorithms
   - Topics include: VGA generation, PIO programming, DMA, networking, audio

## Context7 MCP Server

7. **Context7 MCP for Raspberry Pi Pico Docs**
   - **Server**: `user-context7` or `context7`
   - Use the context7 MCP server to fetch up-to-date Raspberry Pi Pico documentation
   - Query for: RP2040 datasheet, Pico SDK functions, hardware APIs
   - Use when: Need current/live Pico documentation that may have changed
   - **Important**: This server contains ONLY Raspberry Pi Pico documentation, NOT RP6502/Picocomputer documentation

